# @PLUGIN_NAME@

A @CATEGORY_LOWER@ audio plugin built with [Pulp](https://github.com/danielraffel/pulp).

## Building

```bash
cmake -B build
cmake --build build
```

## Plugin Formats

| Format | Location |
|--------|----------|
| VST3 | `build/VST3/@PLUGIN_NAME@.vst3` |
| CLAP | `build/CLAP/@PLUGIN_NAME@.clap` |
| AU | `build/AU/@PLUGIN_NAME@.component` |
| Standalone | `build/@PLUGIN_NAME@` |

